        <scopecontent id="ref1">
            <head>Scope and Content Note</head>
            <p>CWA Local 1060 represents workers at Lucent (formerly Bell Labs, in Murray Hill, NJ). This collection consists of material compiled by Raymond A. Singley (1920-2005), who served as a local steward and executive board member. The collection includes minutes, reports, stewards manuals, bargaining and grievance materials, and CWA memorabilia.</p>
        </scopecontent>
